  schema:name "Garden cress cultivation" ;
  schema:description "Growing protocol for *Lepidium sativum*, the rapid-cycling salad and microgreen crop. Germination to maturity in 15–20 days under optimal cool conditions. Multiple succession plantings (5–8 crops per season) from early spring through fall. Excellent introductory crop for children and rapid microgreen production." ;
